  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  30 to 80 years of age

          -  Receiving hemodialysis at least 12 months and less than 5 years

          -  Pre-dialysis systolic blood pressure was more than 160 mmHg, or more than 150 mmHg if
             the patients received antihypertensive agents.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Use of angiotensin receptor blocker or angiotensin converting enzyme inhibitor
      </textblock>
